{
  "stem": "19837.1",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 522.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I always liked to travel.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we did, as children.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Once a year, mother took us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Father almost never had time, but sometimes he had to back down and go with us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Some resort places and spas.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother had, I think it was called gout, and, you know, for every sickness they had a different spa.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "This aunt had stomach trouble.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She went somewhere else.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And people believed, though, the doctors at that time believed it was the springs and taking baths in the spring water.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that's what we did.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Of course, we children didn't.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We just liked to roam around.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wanted to be a teacher or a social worker.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That was absolutely-- I knew that since I was 12 years old, only I couldn't make up my mind which one.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And then, when I did go through the school that I was eligible to go to the university, they asked me for my religion, and of course I said Jewish.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they said, get out of here.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Jews are not allowed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "18.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Berlin.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "University in Berlin.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] my father said, I was in the first World War, and I won an Iron Cross for bravery.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I'm going to take my Iron Cross and go with you.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They're not going to do that to you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he went with me, and they saw him out too.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So he didn't want to believe it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everything that's happening, what happened, they-- they didn't-- just couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "What was your father in the First World War?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Just, probably-- I don't know even the ranks here.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Just a foot soldier, nothing special.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in-- in-- in the east, in Romania, Russia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's what I always heard.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
